data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Escondido’s coveted Lomas Serenas neighborhood! This meticulously maintained residence is nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac and sits on an expansive half-acre lot. With a sparkling pool, spa, and completely updated interior, it’s a true gem. The home exterior provides unrivaled curb appeal while the interior consists of over 3,700 sq feet of living space. As a bonus, this home offers easy access to the picturesque Lake Hodges, as well as close proximity to shopping and dining. As you enter this home on the main floor, you will be impressed by the vaulted ceilings and the modern floorplan that boasts a spacious family room, master bedroom with a jaw dropping en suite, a beautifully updated kitchen, and a deck for outdoor enjoyment. The added bonus is an office for remote work or creative pursuits, making this level perfect for both relaxation and productivity. Downstairs is designed for entertainment, with a well-appointed bar, a large living room, and a game room that’s ready for fun-filled gatherings. Three additional bedrooms complete this level, providing ample space for family and guests, while easy access to the pool and spa creates a perfect area for entertaining. The expansive yard provides all the space you need, as well as lush landscaping, privacy, a shed for storage, fenced in dog run and unmatched tranquility.
